    "body": "So, this is a subtle thing. Option 3 basically already occurs.\r\n\r\nIn this line:\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/vyper/blob/master/examples/tokens/ERC20.vy#L85\r\n\r\nWe are decrementing the sender's allowance as allocated by `_from`. If that allowance is lower than the amount we want to transfer, the function will revert (because we bake in SafeMath by default).\r\n\r\nShould add a comment there to that effect (and also to `transfer` in line 67 and `transferFrom` in line 83 for balance checking)\r\n\r\n",
